  <brief_title>Effects of Physical Activity on the Brain in Impaired Glucose Tolerance (IGT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exercise in Elderly Individuals With Impaired Glucose Tolerance: Beneficial for Vasculature and Neurons?</official_title>
